Class Management.LogicalRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.persistit.Management.AcquisitionTimeBase
      • com.persistit.Management.LogicalRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Enclosing interface:
    Management

    public static class Management.LogicalRecord
extends Management.AcquisitionTimeBase
implements Serializable
    A structure that contains data about a single logical record within a page. Used by display tools to display the contents of a tree. The method Management.getLogicalRecordArray(java.lang.String, java.lang.String, java.lang.String, com.persistit.KeyState, com.persistit.Key.Direction, int, int, boolean) method returns an array of LogicalRecordInfo elements for a specified page.
